'''2015年单县爆炸案'''于2015年7月20日晚22:34左右发生于[[中华人民共和国|中华人民共和国]][[山东省|山东省]][[菏泽市|菏泽市]][[单县|单县]]的湖西公园西门附近。事发时正值市民在此聚集看戏，嫌疑人解兴堂在现场引爆了自制爆炸物发动自杀式袭击，造成包括其本人在内的两人当场死亡，另有24人受伤，其中一名伤者送医后不治身亡；现场附近的店面和戏台遭到破坏。<ref name="bjnews">{{cite news|url=http://epaper.bjnews.com.cn/html/2015-07/22/content_589305.htm?div=-1|title=山东单县一公园爆炸案致3死24伤|work=新京报|date=2015-07-22|accessdate=2016-06-16|archive-date=2015-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151004020301/http://epaper.bjnews.com.cn/html/2015-07/22/content_589305.htm?div=-1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="DW">{{cite news|url=http://www.dw.com/zh/%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%9C%E5%8D%95%E5%8E%BF%E8%87%AA%E6%9D%80%E5%BC%8F%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%E6%A1%88-%E5%AB%8C%E7%8A%AF%E6%82%A3%E6%9C%89%E8%82%9D%E7%A1%AC%E5%8C%96/a-18597097|title=山东单县自杀式爆炸案 嫌犯患有肝硬化|work=德国之声|date=2015-07-21|accessdate=2016-06-16|archive-date=2016-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160622154215/http://www.dw.com/zh/%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%9C%E5%8D%95%E5%8E%BF%E8%87%AA%E6%9D%80%E5%BC%8F%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%E6%A1%88-%E5%AB%8C%E7%8A%AF%E6%82%A3%E6%9C%89%E8%82%9D%E7%A1%AC%E5%8C%96/a-18597097|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="sina">{{cite news|url=http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2015-07-22/020032132697.shtml|title=山东单县公园爆炸案致3死24伤 嫌犯长年患病|work=新浪新闻|date=2015-07-22|accessdate=2016-06-16|archive-date=2016-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160812041958/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2015-07-22/020032132697.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="qq"/><ref name="theguardian">{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/jul/21/chinese-man-kills-two-including-self-park-bombing|title=China park bombing kills two, injures 24 others|work=The Guardian|date=2015-07-21|accessdate=2016-06-17|archive-date=2016-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160514210300/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/jul/21/chinese-man-kills-two-including-self-park-bombing|dead-url=no}}</ref>
